text: KIEE (88.3 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of St. Martinville, Louisiana. The station is owned by Southern Consumers Education Foundation. It airs a variety radio format. The station was assigned the KIEE call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on August 11, 2011. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * Category:Radio stations in Louisiana Category:Radio stations established in 2011 Category:2011 establishments in Louisiana Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:St. Martin Parish, Louisiana
